about%20returning%20to%20California.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20years%20of%20searching%2C%20she%20purchased%20an%20estate%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-town-testing-everyone-covid-19-bolinas-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBolinas%2C%20California%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%247.5%20million%20in%202019%2C%20as%20first%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Freal-estate%2Fluxury-homes%2Fannie-leibovitz-lists-65-acre-california-farm-ba1e5760%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20month%2C%20she%20listed%20the%20property%20for%20sale%2C%20asking%20%248.995.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20inside%20the%20property%20that%20captured%20this%20famous%20photographer's%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20estate%2C%20nicknamed%20The%20Hideaway%2C%20is%20nestled%20on%2065%20acres%20with%20views%20of%20Bolinas%20Lagoon%2C%20Stinson%20Beach%2C%20Mount%20Tamalpais%2C%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6628221f10dfcda409627147%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%3Cp%3EJacob%20Elliott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20has%20sprawling%20vistas%20of%20rolling%20hills%20and%20verdant%20pastures.%20It's%20located%20near%20bird%20and%20seal%20sanctuaries%20and%20is%20about%20an%20hour%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-throws-festival-toilet-cost-200k-noe-valley-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Considered%20a%20historical%20touchpoint%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20property%20sits%20near%20the%20small%20coast