%20make%20her%20home%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%20and%20when%20she%20purchased%20the%20property%2C%20she%20thought%20she'd%20found%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20told%20of%20this%20extraordinary%20property%20that%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hill%20had%20views%20of%20the%20lagoon%20and%20bay%20and%20the%20coast%20that%20are%20magnificent.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20special%20climate%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20can%20grow%20year%20round.%20There%20were%2065%20acres%20with%20an%20old%20milking%20barn%20that%20Ansel%20Adams%20had%20photographed.%20It%20had%20been%20used%20as%20a%20gathering%20place%20for%20country%20and%20folk%20music%20concerts%20in%20its%20day.%20We%20planned%20to%20partner%20with%20a%20legendary%20farmer%20over%20the%20hill%20to%20bring%20the%20place%20back%20to%20its%20former%20self%20as%20a%20working%20and%20teaching%20farm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELeibovitz%20remodeled%20portions%20of%20the%20property%20but%20kept%20key%20fixtures%20like%20this%20rotary%20phone.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20rotary%20phone%20that%20still%20hangs%20on%20the%20wall%20in%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66272dd40dfb1341e9fdd051%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20rotary%20phone%20that%20still%20hangs%20on%20the%20wall%20in%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%3Cp%3EJacob%20Elliott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20spent%20many%20holidays%20with%20friends%20in%20Bolinas%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20children%20were%20born%20we%20would%20go%20together%20and%20they%20would%20surf%20and%20pick%20up%20shells%20and%20stones%20along%20the%20shore.%20And%20I%20would%20occasionally%20look%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20her