%20to%20reach%20her%20life%20goals%20after%20paying%20off%20over%20%2450%2C000%20in%20debt.%20Anat%20found%20herself%20in%20%2442%2C000%20of%20student%20loan%20debt%20and%20added%20another%20%2412%2C000%20in%20credit%20card%20debt%20after%20moving%20to%20New%20York.%20Anat%20writes%20that%20she%20taught%20herself%20how%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20debt%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bbudgeting%20unlocked%20all%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20my%20adult%20life.%26quot%3B%20This%20includes%20saving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnat%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BSaving%20money%20unlocks%20your%20wildest%20dreams.%20And%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20whether%20your%20dream%20is%20to%20buy%20stuff%2C%20buy%20experiences%2C%20or%20buy%20time%2C%20everyone%20is%20saving%20money%20for%20one%20thing%3A%20freedom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20save%20money%20to%20get%20free%20and%20that%20is%20what%20your%20savings%20should%20do%20for%20you.%20Financial%20freedom%20looks%20different%20to%20everyone%2C%20but%20you%20will%20not%20get%20there%20without%20saving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20save%20money%20the%20right%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20find%20saving%20tedious%20or%20punitive%20when%20you're%20saving%20just%20to%20save.%20Saving%20is%20a%20tool%20to%20help%20you%20meet%20your%20financial%20and%20life%20goals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20can%20decide%20ahead%20of%20time%20how%20that%20money%20will%20be%20used.%20Anat%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20get%20very%20specific%20about%20your%20saving%20goals.%20Give%20yourself%20direction%20by%20having%20very%20specific%20goals%20you%20are%20saving%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaving%20money%20is%20the%20ultimate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpay-yourself-first%5C%22%3Epay-yourself-first%3C%2Fa%3E%20move%2C%20and%20being%20specific%20about%20what%20you%20are%20saving%20for%20gives%20you%20something%20tangible%20to%20reach%20for.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20depo