%3EAnna%20Sawai%20as%20Toda%20Mariko%20in%20%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EKatie%20Yu%2FFX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFX's%C2%A0%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20historical%20drama%20set%20in%20Edo-era%20Japan%2C%20has%20come%20to%20a%20close.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20its%20creators%2C%20the%20show%20has%20told%20the%20story%20it%20intended%20to%20tell.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20some%20viewers%20still%20want%20more.%20Here's%20everything%20we%20know%20about%20a%20possible%20season%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFX's%20%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20historical%20drama%20set%20in%20Edo-era%20Japan%2C%20tracking%20a%20power%20struggle%20further%20muddied%20by%20the%20arrival%20of%20a%20foreigner%2C%20who%20may%20be%20a%20powerful%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series%2C%20created%20by%20Rachel%20Kondo%20and%20Justin%20Marks%2C%20is%20based%20on%20James%20Clavell's%201975%20novel.%20It%20stars%20Hiroyuki%20Sanada%20as%20Lord%20Toranaga%2C%20a%20figure%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20real-life%20sh%C5%8Dgun%20(military%20ruler)%20of%20Japan%2C%20Tokugawa%20Ieyasu.%20When%20a%20foreign%20pilot%20named%20John%20Blackthorne%20(Cosmo%20Jarvis)%20washes%20ashore%2C%20Toranaga%20realizes%20that%20he%20may%20have%20political%20utility.%20Toda%20Mariko%2C%20played%20by%20Anna%20Sawai%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20translator%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rottentomatoes.com%2Ftv%2Fshogun_2024%2Fs01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20many%20critics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20been%20loving%20%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun%2C%26quot%3B%20there's%20a%20chance%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20the%20story%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20book%20and%20put%20a%20period%20at%20the%20end%20of%20that%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20Marks%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Ftv%2Ftv-features%2Fshogun-feudal-japan-season-2-chances-showrunners-interview-1235845407%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20love%20how%20the%20book%20ends%3B%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20we%20both%20knew%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20we%20ended%20in%20exactly%20that%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20show%20has%20been%20wildly%20successful%20for%20FX.%20And%20while%20there's%20no%20official%20word%20yet%20on%20how%20things%20will%20pan%20out%2C%C2%A0here's%20everything%20we%20know%20about%20whether%20the%20show%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHas%20'Sh%C5%8Dgun'%20been%20renewed%20for%20season%202%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20yet%2C%20but%20don't%20lose%20all%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20THR%20asked%20Marks%20to%20clarify%20whether%20his%20comments%20precluded%20a%20second%20season%2C%20he%20didn't%20immediately%20shut%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20that's%20just%20our%20bodies%20talking.%20Like%2C%20do%20you%20want%20to%20have%20another%20kid%20right%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20we%20also%20made%20this%20show%20so%20long%20ago%2C%20because%20of%20the%20long%20tail%20of%20postproduction%20on%20it.%20It's%20not%20like%20a%20normal%20TV%20series%2C%20where%20if%20we%20were%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20this%20promoting%20it%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20just%20be%20in%20the%20writers%20room%20already%2C%20we'd%20be%20on%20set%20shooting%20season%20two%20by%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Maria%20Gonzales%2C%20one%20of%20the%20show's%20editors%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcomicbook.com%2Ftv-shows%2Fnews%2Fshogun-season-2-release-date-renewed-canceled-editors-interview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EComicBook%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20crew%20hadn't%20explicitly%20discussed%20a%20second%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20of%20completing%2C%20when%20we%20were%20done%20cutting%2C%20there%20wasn't%20really%20any%20mention%20of%2C%20or%20any%20serious%20plans%20about%20a%20season%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20Gonzales%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20that's%20kind%20of%20where%20we're%20at%20still.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20it%20will%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20might%20'Sh%C5%8Dgun'%20season%202%20premiere%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDifficult%20to%20say.%20While%20a%20second%20season%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20require%20the%20same%20level%20of%20research%20and%20preparation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Marks%20told%20THR%20that%20the%20show's%20%26quot%3Bproduction%20primer%20on%20feudal%20Japan%26quot%3B%20could%20save%20another%20show%20almost%20a%20year's%20time%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20first%20season%20of%20Sh%C5%8Dgun%20was%20a%20five-year%20journey%2C%20Marks%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.townandcountrymag.com%2Fleisure%2Farts-and-culture%2Fa46871997%2Fshogun-season-2-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETown%20%26amp%3B%20Country%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20per%20Marks'%20comments%2C%20continuing%20onwards%20would%20mean%20diverging%20from%20Clavell's%20road%20map%20since%20the%20source%20material%20only%20consists%20of%20one%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOkay%2C%20so%20what%20%3Cem%3Ecould%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20the%20source%20material%20for%20a%20second%20season%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20self-contained%20novel.%20But%20Clavell%20wrote%20a%20series%20of%20novels%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BAsian%20Saga%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20follow%20the%20meeting%20of%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20other%20novels%20in%20the%20series%3A%20%26quot%3BKing%20Rat%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTai-Pan%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BNoble%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhirlwind%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BGai-Jin%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20from%201962%20to%201993.%20They're%20set%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20countries%20and%20time%20periods%2C%20including%20the%20more%20recent%20past%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%26quot%3BKing%20Rat%26quot%3B%20takes%20place%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20and%20draws%20from%20Clavell's%20personal%20experience%20as%20a%20prisoner%20of%20war.%20%26quot%3BTai-Pan%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20next%20novel%2C%20takes%20place%20in%2019th-century%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20it's%20impossible%20to%20tell%20where%20a%20second%20season%20would%20go.%20If%20the%20show%20wanted%20to%20follow%20Clavell's%20work%2C%20it%20could%20take%20an%20anthology%20approach.%20Or%2C%20it%20could%20extrapolate%20past%20the%20original%20%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun%26quot%3B%20novel%20and%20decide%20what's%20next%20for%20the%20show's%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun%26quot%3B%20season%20one%20is%20now%20available%20to%20stream%20in%20its%20entirety%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D4b049efd4300c73fcd2813e2732eb998f3bf3dcd4b319808cca6b2a38a41bfb7%26postID%3D662283b297126ae3b20e12f4%26postSlug%3Dshogun-season-2-renewal-release-date-cast-trailer-2024-4%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hulu.com%252Fwelcome%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHulu%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshogun-season-2-renewal-release-date-cast-trailer-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713907221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622a41b0dfb1341e9fd1e5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshogun-season-2-renewal-release-date-cast-trailer-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%26quot%3BShogun%26quot%3B%20season%20finale%20just%20aired%20and%20while%20it%20hasn't%20been%20renewed%20for%20season%202%20yet%2C%20all%20hope%20isn't%20lost.%20The%20creators%20haven