%20and%20Jessica%20Gunning%20as%20Martha%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEd%20Miller%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERichard%20Gadd%20based%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20experience%20of%20being%20stalked%20and%20sexually%20abused.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGadd%20plays%20a%20version%20of%20himself%20in%20the%20show%20and%20concealed%20the%20identities%20of%20his%20stalker%20and%20abuser.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20are%20trying%20to%20deduce%20who%20the%20real-life%20people%20are%2C%20and%20Gadd%20has%20asked%20them%20to%20stop.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix's%20latest%20hit%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%2C%26quot%3B%20written%20by%20and%20starring%20Richard%20Gadd%2C%20is%20a%20lightly%20fictionalized%20true%20story%20based%20on%20Gadd's%20actual%20experience%20of%20being%20stalked%20and%20sexually%20abused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20limited%20series%2C%20which%20Gadd%20adapted%20from%20his%20one-man%20stage%20show%20of%20the%20same%20name%2C%20Gadd%20plays%20Donny%20Dunn%2C%20a%20fictionalized%20version%20of%20himself.%20Donny%20is%20stalked%20by%20an%20older%20woman%20named%20Martha%20Scott%20(played%20by%20Jessica%20Gunning)%2C%20who%20is%20based%20on%20Gadd's%20real%20stalker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20also%20deals%20with%20Donny's%20grooming%20and%20sexual%20assault%20by%20an%20older%20male%20comedy%20writer%20he%20admired%20named%20Darrien%20(Tom%20Goodman-Hill)%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20difficulty%20he%20had%20coming%20to%20terms%20with%20his%20bisexuality%20after%20his%20abuse.%20This%2C%20too%2C%20is%20based%20on%20what%20happened%20to%20Gadd%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20legal%20reasons%2C%20Gadd%20hasn't%20revealed%20the%20real%20identity%20of%20his%20stalker%2C%20or%20the%20writer%20Darrien%20was%20based%20on.%20But%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20viewers%20from%20trying%20to%20figure%20it%20out%20and%20speculating%20about%20the%20characters'%20real%20identities%20on%20social%20media.%20Now%2C%20the%20writer%20and%20actor%20is%20addressing%20the%20fans%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20play%20detective%20and%20telling%20them%20to%20quit%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHi%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Gadd%20wrote%20in%20an%20Instagram%20story%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20I%20love%2C%20have%20worked%20with%2C%20and%20admire%20(including%20Sean%20Foley)%20are%20unfairly%20getting%20caught%20up%20in%20speculation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BPlease%20don't%20speculate%20on%20who%20any%20of%20the%20real-life%20people%20could%20be.%20That's%20not%20the%20point%20of%20our%20show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Gadd's%20statement%20about%20Baby%20Reindeer%20on%20Instagram%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6627fa6610dfcda409624d64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221685%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGadd%20made%20a%20statement%20on%20Instagram%20Monday.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Gadd%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Foley%2C%20a%20British%20writer%2C%20director%2C%20comedian%2C%20and%20actor%2C%20also%20addressed%20the%20rampant%20speculation%20that%20he%20was%20Gadd's%20abuser%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20shared%20hours%20after%20Gadd's%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolice%20have%20been%20informed%20and%20are%20investigating%20all%20defamatory%20abusive%20and%20threatening%20posts%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Foley%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSeanFoleyJ%2Fstatus%2F1782655837489492126%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1782655837489492126%257Ctwgr%255E94737f6af06e754efd7af3c0805fb7691cd5d117%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.standard.co.uk%252Fshowbiz%252Fbaby-reindeer-police-investigation-false-accusations-richard-gadd-abuser-b1153263.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5