%20food%2C%20is%20the%20restaurant%20still%20delivering%20hits%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20coasting%20on%20its%20legacy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECecconi's%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20Soho%20House%2C%20has%20been%20in%20West%20Hollywood%20for%2015%20years.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecconi's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d7cf93f923f7dab0816d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20Cecconi's.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECecconi's%20has%20always%20been%20a%20magnet%20for%20the%20A-list%20and%20princes.%20Enzo%20Cecconi%20opened%20the%20first%20location%20in%201978%2C%20bringing%20%26quot%3Bfresh%20pasta%2C%20beef%20carpaccio%2C%20tiramisu%2C%20and%20Bellini%20cocktails%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20British%2C%20according%20to%20the%20restaurant's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cecconis.co.uk%2Fhistory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoho%20House%20took%20full%20ownership%20in%202005%2C%20and%20now%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohohouse.com%2Fen-us%2Frestaurants%2Fcecconis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13%20Cecconi's%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20world%2C%20stretching%20from%20Miami%20Beach%20to%20Mumbai.%20But%20the%20West%20Hollywood%20iteration%20is%20the%20most%20well-known%20thanks%20to%20its%20star-studded%20clientele%2C%20earning%20it%20a%20spot%20alongside%20classic%20LA%20establishments%20like%20Spago%2C%20The%20Ivy%2C%20and%20Polo%20Lounge%20as%20a%20place%20to%20%26quot%3Bsee%20and%20be%20seen%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20cut%20some%20good%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20in%20LA%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%20but%20had%20never%20dined%20at%20Cecconi's.%20It%20was%20time%20to%20see%20a%20true%20power%20lunch%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20gloomy%20sky%20greeted%20me%20as%20I%20arrived%20for%20lunch%20on%20a%20Friday%20afternoon.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecconi's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d7e6716bde8d4ead926eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECecconi's%20has%20a%20tented%20outdoor%20dining%20area%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20patio.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20and%20I%20had%20no%20trouble%20getting%20a%20table%2C%20realizing%20why%20as%20we%20walked%20up%20the%20driveway%20and%20into%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20ample%20seating%20throughout%20the%20airy%20space%2C%20including%20a%20nearly%20empty%20tented%20dining%20area%20in%20front%20of%20the%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20patio%20was%20nearly%20full%20as%20we%20walked%20up%20to%20the%20hostess.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecconi's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d7e4d3f923f7dab0817e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20patio%20lunch%20crowd%20had%20dispersed%20by%20the%20time%20I%20snapped%20this%20photo%20on%20our%20way%20out.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20surprised%20when%20the%20hostess%20asked%20for%20my%20number%2C%20wondering%20if%20we%20should've%20made%20a%20reservation.%20But%20she%20explained%20it%20was%20actually%20to%20help%20return%20any%20lost%20items.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20wouldn't%20believe%20what%20people%20leave%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BGucci%20bags%2C%20iPads%2C%20Louis%20Vuitton%20duffels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBright%20pops%20of%20color%20and%20a%20bold%20floor%20gave%20the%20restaurant%20a%20more%20modern%20vibe%20than%20I%20expected.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecconi's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d7e3716bde8d4ead9264e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPart%20of%20Cecconi's%20dining%20room.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bpower%20lunch%26quot%3B%20can%20bring%20to%20mind%20a%20vision%20of%20stuffy%20and%20dated%20interiors%2C%20but%20I%20loved%20the%20leather%20turquoise%20chairs%20and%20black-and-white%20striped%20floor%20in%20Cecconi's%20dining%20room.%20They%20added%20a%20chic%20touch%20alongside%20the%20old-school%20chandeliers%20and%20dark%20wood%20paneling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20seated%20next%20to%20the%20wraparound%20bar%20in%20front%20of%20one%20of%20the%20doors%20that%20opened%20up%20to%20the%20patio.%20It%20was%20a%20perfect%20people-watching%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20might%20have%20been%20power%20lunch%20hour%2C%20few%20people%20were%20in%20suits%20or%20business%20casual.%20Two%20very%20glamorous%20older%20women%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0perfectly%20coiffed%20hair%2C%20gold%20jewelry%2C%20Jackie%20O%20sunglasses%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0sat%20across%20from%20us.%20A%20group%20of%20friends%20in%20jeans%20and%20sweaters%20were%20laughing%20nearby.%20A%20handful%20of%20solo%20diners%20were%20enjoying%20quiet%20meals%20at%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECecconi's%20extensive%20menu%20features%20pizza%2C%20pasta%2C%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20appetizers%20and%20entr%C3%A9es.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecconi's%20menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d7d1b16bde8d4ead924b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECecconi's%20menu.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20highlights%20of%20our%20lunch%20was%20the%20extremely%20kind%20waiter%2C%20who%20highly%20recommended%20we%20get%20a%20pizza%20%E2%80%94%20which%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20best%20dish%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20heard%20there%20was%20a%20secret%20Cecconi's%20burger%2C%20but%20our%20waiter%20revealed%20it%20only%20makes%20special%20appearances%20(usually%20during%20happy%20hour).%20I%20also%20inquired%20about%20the%20%2426%20%26quot%3BPiatto%20Unico%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20which%20we%20learned%20is%20a%20lunchtime%20special%20that%20changes%20weekly%20and%20always%20features%20a%20protein%2C%20side%2C%20and%20salad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20worth%20trying%20that%20week's%20special%2C%20our%20waiter%20recommended%20we%20go%20with%20an%20appetizer%20and%20two%20dishes%20instead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20kicked%20things%20off%20with%20a%20%2422%20Peach%20Bourbon%20Smash%20cocktail.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecconi's%20Peach%20Smash%20cocktail%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d7d351caec1275a704d66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20Peach%20Bourbon%20Smash%20cocktail.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EListed%20as%20one%20of%20Cecconi's%20seasonal%20cocktails%2C%20the%20Peach%20Bourbon%20Smash%20is%20made%20with%20Maker's%20Mark%2C%20lemon%2C%20ginger%2C%20peach%2C%20and%20strawberry%20bitters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20drink%20had%20a%20lovely%20sunny%20hue%20that%20brightened%20up%20the%20very%20cloudy%20LA%20day%2C%20with%20flavors%20to%20match.%20It%20was%20a%20sweet%20and%20zingy%20drink%2C%20and%20the%20ginger%20candy%20garnish%20was%20a%20fun%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20came%20the%20%2428%20grilled%20octopus%2C%20which%20is%20served%20with%20lemon%2C%20capers%2C%20and%20olives.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecconi's%20octopus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d7d511caec1275a704db7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20octopus%20was%20far%20too%20charred.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-greek-pasta-dish-thats-better-than-lasagna-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimmigrated%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Greece%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20a%20love%20for%20octopus%20is%20ingrained%20in%20me.%20A%20great%20plate%20can%20immediately%20transport%20me%20back%20to%20childhood%20summer%20days%20spent%20in%20tavernas%20overlooking%20the%20Aegean%20Sea%2C%20our%20table%20covered%20in%20a%20seafood%20feast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECecconi's%20octopus%20unfortunately%20didn't%20live%20up%20to%20those%20memories%2C%20nor%20did%20it%20come%20close%20to%20some%20fantastic%20plates%20I've%20had%20on%20recent%20trips%20to%20Mexico%20(Ziggy's%20octopus%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpablo-escobar-former-mansion-resort-tulum-photos-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETulum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20you).%20The%20octopus%20had%20a%20soft%20texture%20%E2%80%94%20no%20easy%20feat%20with%20such%20a%20tricky%20protein.%20But%20the%20meat%20was%20so%20charred%20on%20the%20outside%20that%20it%20completely%20overwhelmed%20the%20flavor.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServed%20alongside%20peppadew%20peppers%2C%20which%20added%20a%20kick%20of%20heat%2C%20the%20octopus%20was%20begging%20for%20something%20to%20brighten%20up%20the%20plate%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0whether%20it%20be%20a%20cooling%20sauce%20or%20a%20bigger%20splash%20of%20acidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3