Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy's%20promise%20of%20waiving%20Rs%202%20lakh%20loans%20of%20farmers%20before%20August%2015%20was%20made%20two%20days%20ago%20in%20Bhongir.%20BRS%20leader%20and%20nephew%20of%20KCR%2C%20T%20Harish%20Rao%2C%20had%20asked%20yesterday%20whether%20Mr%20Reddy%20would%20resign%20if%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20fulfil%20his%20loan%20waiver%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20was%20Revanth%20Reddy's%20turn%20to%20retort%20and%20he%20asked%20if%20KCR%20would%20disband%20his%20party%20if%20he%20kept%20his%20word%20on%20waiving%20farmer%20loans%20by%20August%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20uncle%20knows%20better%20than%20you%20that%20Revanth%20does%20what%20he%20says%20and%20keeps%20his%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Revanth%20Reddy%20is%20talking%20about%20hanging%20Mr%20Rao.%20A%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20he%20said%20it%20would%20not%20be%20wrong%20to%20hang%20KCR%20and%20his%20son%20for%20the%20way%20in%20which%20they%20had%20allegedly%20looted%20real%20estate%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%206%2C%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20in%20Tukkuguda%2C%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20had%20attacked%20KCR%2C%20declaring%20that%20he%20would%20send%20him%20to%20jail.%20He%20would%20also%20build%20a%202BHK%20for%20Mr%20Rao%20in%20Cherlapally%20so%20he%20could%20cool%20his%20heels%20inside%20with%20his%20family%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20just%20an%20year%20after%20KCR%20became%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20then%20with%20the%20TDP%2C%20went%20to%20jail%20in%20a%20cash-for-votes%20scam.%20He%20had%20to%20come%20out%20on%20bail%20to%20attend%20his%20daughter's%20engagement%20ceremony.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20had%20vowed%20revenge%20against%20KCR%20when%20he%20came%20out%20of%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713900240000%2C%22visual