ies%20vote%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20on%20Friday%2C%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20claimed%20that%2C%20contrary%20to%20its%20aim%20of%20winning%20400%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20will%20not%20cross%20even%20220%20and%20at%20least%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20this%20will%20be%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20not%20fulfilled%20his%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20also%20said%20that%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda's%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bunholy%20one%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20people%20claiming%20that%20Siddaramaiah's%20personality%20is%20important%20in%20an%20Assembly%20election%20but%20PM%20Modi's%20image%20may%20have%20an%20edge%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20image%20that%20he%20(the%20PM)%20has%3F%20When%20he%20has%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20the%20promises%20he%20has%20made%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%20how%20will%20the%20same%20image%20continue%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20a%20Modi%20wave%20in%20the%20entire%20country%2C%20and%20particularly%20in%20Karnataka.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20he%20saw%20the%20Congress'%20prospects%20in%20his%20home%20turf%20of%20Old%20Mysuru%2C%20which%20had%20given%20the%20party%20the%20lone%20seat%20it%20had%20won%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20-%20against%20the%20BJP's%2025%20-%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20the%20situation%20was%20different%20at%20the%20time%20because%20emotional%20issues%20were%20projected.%20In%20these%20elections%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20PM%20has%20to%20list%20his%20achievements%20in%20his%2010-year%20tenure%2C%20and%20also%20predicted%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%2020%20constituencies%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20not%20at%20a%20disadvantage%20despite%20not%20declaring%20a%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20also%20said%20there%20is%20no%20threat%20to%20the%20stability%20of%20his%20government%20irrespective%20of%20the%20election%20results.%20Asked%20if%20the%20Congress%20would%20complete%20its%20term%20in%20the%20state%20regardless%20of%20who%20the%20chief%20minister%20would%20be%2C%20he%20answered%20in%20the%20affirmative%20and%20also%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20party%20would%20get%20another%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstability%20will%20come%20only%20when%20the%20people%20are%20unhappy.%20Stability%20does%20not%20mean%20a%20government%20continuing%20for%2010%20years.%20People%20should%20also%20be%20socially%2C%20politically%20and%20economically%20empowered%2C%20only%20then%20can%20we%20say%20that%20the%20country%20is%20stable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20JD(S)%20and%20the%20BJP%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bunholy%26quot%3B%20one%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20indicated%20that%20it%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%20desperation%20of%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda%20-%20whose%20party%20won%20only%2019%20of%20224%20seats%20in%20last%20year's%20Assembly%20polls%20-%20given%20that%20he%20had%20earlier%20criticised%20PM%20Modi%20on%20several%20issues%2C%20including%20communalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20never%20forget%20what%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20has%20said%20about%20PM%20Modi%20and%20they%20know%20why%20the%20parties%20have%20forged%20an%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713898680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4dl8iq5g_siddaramaiah_625x300_03_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-bjp-will-not-cross-even-220-lok-sabha-seats-siddaramai