20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20claimed%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20India%20as%20a%20voice%20of%20the%20'Global%20South'%20(comprising%20about%20125%20countries)%2C%20he%20said%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20trust%20India%20to%20take%20up%20their%20cause%20and%20positions%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20at%20a%20talk%20on%20'Foreign%20Policy%20the%20India%20Way%3A%20From%20Diffidence%20to%20Confidence'%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20country%20has%20a%20moral%20obligation%20towards%20some%20of%20the%20countries%2C%20which%20were%20under%20colonial%20rule%20and%20could%20not%20recover%2C%20rebuild%20as%20quickly%20as%20India%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20which%20is%20about%20a%20125%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20These%20countries%20trust%20India%20to%20take%20up%20their%20cause%2C%20their%20positions%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20has%20some%20challenges%20at%20the%20borders%20and%20the%20key%20to%20defend%20them%20is%20not%20to%20just%20posture%20in%20public%20but%20to%20build%20infrastructure%2C%20support%20the%20military%20and%20create%20a%20system%20that%20will%20respond%20whenever%20the%20border%20is%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%26quot%3Bdefensive%20era%26quot%3B%2C%20terrorism%20was%20accepted%2C%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20previous%20UPA%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Mumbai%20(attacks)%2C%20the%20national%20security%20advisor%20of%20the%20previous%20UPA%20government%20wrote%20(that)%20'we%20sat%2C%20we%20debated.%20We%20considered%20all%20the%20options.%20Then%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20nothing.%20We%20decided%20to%20do%20nothing%20and%20the%20justification%20was%20we%20felt%20the%20cost%20of%20attacking%20Pakistan%20was%20more%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20not%20attacking%20Pakistan'%2C%20%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20leave%20you%20to%20judge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20the%20foreign%20policy%20moved%20from%20the%20times%20of%20%26quot%3Bdiffidence%26quot%3B%20to%20confidence%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20moved%20from%20diffidence%20to%20confidence%20when%20we%20crossed%20that%20line%20of%20control.%20And%2C%20we%20did%20it%20again%2C%20when%20we%20crossed%20the%20boundary%20to%20go%20and%20hit%20Balakot%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20now%20deals%20with%20the%20United%20States%20much%20more%20confidently%20than%20it%20used%20to%20deal%20before%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20should%20the%20country%20be%20exporting%20BrahMos%20missiles%20to%20other%20countries%20as%20well%2C%20after%20the%20Philippines%2C%20he%20said%20it%20is%20a%20very%20good%20example%20how%20Make%20in%20India%20and%20defence%20has%20got%20the%20country%20an%20important%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20BrahMos.%20It%20would%20be%20other%20equipment%20as%20well.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20new%20area%20that%20India%20is%20entering.%20(PM)%20Modi%20ji%20has%20been%20very%20strongly%20motivating%20our%20defence%20producers%20saying%20we%20are%20good%20enough%20today%20to%20go%20out%20in%20the%20world.%20So%2C%20I%20am%20very%20confident%20that%20our%20defence%20exports%20will%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713895320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkjhcoll_s-jaishankar-ani_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fupa-debated-decided-to-do-nothing-after-2008-attacks-claims-s-jaishankar-5507960%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20previous%20UPA%20government%20decided%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20do%20anyth