mponent%20attached%20to%20the%20practice.%20The%20trend%20is%20now%20being%20called%20%26quot%3BQuit-Tok%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fworklife%2Farticle%2F20230321-quittok-why-young-workers-are-live-quitting-on-tiktok%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20these%20videos%20captures%20real-time%20moment%20when%20workers%20resign.%20It%20can%20take%20several%20forms-%20it%20could%20be%20departure%20on%20a%20Zoom%20call%20or%20when%20they%20hand%20the%20letter%20of%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Australian%20government%20employee%20Christina%20Zumbo%20described%20in%20September%202022%20the%20moment%20she%20sent%20out%20her%20resignation%20email%20and%20nervously%20awaited%20her%20boss's%20video%20call.%20After%20revealing%20snippets%20of%20her%20issues%20with%20mental%20health%20related%20to%20her%20job%20to%20her%20140%2C000%20TikTok%20followers%2C%20Ms%20Zumbo%20said%20she%20thought%20other%20users%20would%20be%20able%20to%20identify%20with%20the%20post%2C%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20struggled%20with%20making%20this%20decision%20to%20leave%2C%20feeling%20like%20I%20was%20letting%20my%20team%20and%20manager%20down%2C%20and%20the%20thought%20of%20being%20without%20work%20without%20something%20lined%20up%2C%20into%20a%20tumultuous%20job%20market%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20decided%20to%20share%20this%20journey%20online%20because%20it%20simply%20isn't%20talked%20about%20enough.%26quot%3B%20She%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20idea%20so%20many%20people%20would%20see%2C%20relate%20and%20share%20their%20own%20stories%20-%20or%20their%20fear%20of%20leaving%20their%20current%20workplace%2C%20or%20their%20strong%20desire%20to%20do%20what%20I%20did.%20It's%20always%20surprising%20in%20the%20best%20way%2C%20the%20sense%20of%20community%20you%20feel%20if%20you%20open%20yourself%20up%20to%20showing%20real%2C%20relatable%20vulnerability%20online.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20employees%20might%20find%20the%20experience%20entertaining%20or%20fulfilling%20at%20the%20time%2C%20job%20experts%20say%20that%20those%20TikTokers%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20craze%20now%20regret%20it.%20They%20warn%20that%20there%20are%20serious%20long-term%20repercussions.%20Paige%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20hospitality%20worker%20from%20Florida%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Flifestyle%2Fquit-tok-viral-younger-workers-job-experts-caution-public-pronouncements%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20made%20fun%20of%20her%20previous%20employer%20on%20TikTok%20after%20being%20asked%20to%20stay%20late%20at%20events%20on%20several%20occasions%20while%20other%20%26quot%3Bfavoured%26quot%3B%20employees%20were%20allowed%20to%20go.%20She%20quit%20her%20job%20live%20on%20TikTok%20and%20now%20she%20regrets%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20the%20mature%20thing%20to%20do%20and%20my%20parents%20were%20on%20my%20back%20about%20it.%20I%20now%20have%20a%20new%20job.%20It%20seems%20like%20a%20cool%20way%20to%20show%20that%20you%20have%20power%20over%20others%20but%20the%20next%20day%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20stupid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeil%20Costa%2C%20the%20Boston-based%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20HireCli%20said%20that%20this%20behaviour%20%26quot%3Bwould%20come%20at%20a%20cost.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20world%20of%20work%20is%20much%20smaller%20than%20you'd%20think.%20As%20the%20way%20we%20look%20at%20work%20shifts%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20blurring%20the%20lines%20between%20personal%20and%20professional%2C%20it's%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20for%20employees%20to%20think%20through%20the%20potential%20long-term%20repercussions%20of%20posting%20on%20the%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJessica%20Roper%2C%20director%20of%20career%20services%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Phoenix%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20reality%20that%20employers%20today%20are%20making%20fewer%20hires.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20job%20market%20is%20increasingly%20competitive.%20Workers%20are%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%2C%20so%20it%20is%20a%20difficult%20environment%20in%20which%20to%20be%20choosing%20to%20burn%20bridges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Costa%20said%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20quit%20is%20to%20inform%20your%20manager%20via%20an%20email%20or%20letter.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20done%20good%20work%2C%20there%20is%20always%20an%20opportunity%20for%20your%20colleagues%20and%20managers%20to%20want%20to%20work%20with%20you%20again%2C%20opening%20future%20opportunities%20that%20may%20not%20be%20available%20to%20you%20if%20you%20engage%20in%20Quit-Tok%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Costa%20told%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713889320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fc0b6nltg_resign_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwhat-is-quit-tok-the-viral-trend-where-workers-live-quit-on-tiktok-5507632%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20these%20employees%20might%20find%20the%20experience%20entertaining%20or%20fulfilling%20at%20the%20time%2C%20job%20experts%20say%20that%20those%20TikTokers%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20craze%20now%20regret%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwhat-is-quit-tok-the-viral-trend-where-workers-live-quit-on-tiktok-5507632%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwhat-is-quit-tok-the-viral-trend-where-workers-live-quit-on-tiktok-5507632%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwhat-is-quit-tok-the-viral-trend-where-workers-live-quit-on-tiktok-5507632%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Losing%20all%20credibility'%3A%20Judge%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%20lawyer%20in%20hush%20money%20trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713889229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109539770%2Cimgsize-90870.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flosing-all-credibility-judge-to-donald-trumps-lawyer-in-hush-money-trial%2Farticleshow%2F109538796.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109538796.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDuring%20Trump's%20hush%20money%20trial%2C%20judge%20Merchan%20criticized%20Todd%20Blanche%20for%20lacking%20evidence.%20Prosecutor%20Conroy%20seeks%20a%20%2410%2C000%20fine%20for%20Trump%20violating%20the%20gag%20order%2C%20potentially%20impacting%20his%20candidacy%20for%20the%20Nov.%205%20election%20against%20Joe%20Biden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flosing-all-credibility-judge-to-donald-trumps-lawyer-in-hush-money-trial%2Farticleshow%2F109538796.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flosing-all-credibility-judge-to-donald-trumps-lawyer-in-hush-money-trial%2Famp_articleshow%2F109538796.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flosing-all-credibility-judge-to-donald-trumps-lawyer-in-hush-money-trial%2Famp_articleshow%2F109538796.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20In%2017%20Years!%20Gaikwad%20Breaks%20Dhoni's%20Record%20For%20Big%20Feat%20In%20IPL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108591-ruturaj-gaikwad-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERuturaj%20Gaikwad%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shivam%20Dube%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107521-shivam-dubey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fa%3E%20absolutely%20owned%20the%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20bowlers%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20take%20their%20team%20to%20a%20score%20of%20210%2F4%20in%2020%20overs.%20Gaikwad%20slammed%20an%20unbeaten%20ton%20while%20Shivam%20Dube%20struck%20a%20quick-fore%2066%20as%20CSK%20made%20merry%20at%20the%20MA%20Chidambaram%20Stadium.%20To%20add%20to%20the%20CSK%20fans'%20joy%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20out%20to%20bat%20too%20and%20finished%20off%20in%20style%20by%20hitting%20a%20boundary.%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20CSK%20captaincy%20from%20Dhoni%20this%20season%2C%20stayed%20unbeaten%20on%20108*.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20a%20CSK%20captain%20has%20struck%20a%20century%20in%20the%20IPL.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20highest%20score%20by%20a%20CSK%20captain%20in%20the%20IPL.%20MS%20Dhoni's%20highest%20in%20the%20IPL%20is%2084*.%20However%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20Gaikwad%20is%20an%20opener%20while%20Dhoni%20batter%20in%20the%20middle%20order%20and%2C%20hence%2C%20always%20had%20lesser%20number%20of%20balls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20remarkable%20unbeaten%20hundred%20by%20captain%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20and%20Shivam%20Dube's%20ruthless%20fifty%20formed%20the%20pillars%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings'%20competitive%20210%20for%20four%20against%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants.%20Gaikwad%20(108%2C%2060b%2C%2012x4%2C%203x6)%20and%20Dube%20(66%2C%2027b%2C%203x4%2C%207x6)%20added%20104%20runs%20for%20an%20entertaining%20fourth-wicket%20stand%20that%20gave%20steam%20to%20Super%20Kings%20innings%20after%20a%20rather%20subdued%20Power%20Play%20(49%2F2)%20and%20the%20middle%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSK%20should%20primarily%20thank%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20played%20an%20innings%20which%20was%20a%20connoisseur's%20delight%2C%20for%20that%20total%20after%20the%20early%20departure%20of%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%2C%20who%20was%20caught%20superbly%20by%20stumper%20KL%20Rahul%20off%20Matt%20Henry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20batting%20in%20this%20iteration%20of%20the%20IPL%20has%20been%20all%20about%20scorching%20the%20ball%20far%20and%20wide%20but%20Gaikwad%20took%20a%20classic%20route%2C%20timing%20the%20ball%20through%20the%20gaps%20for%20fours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20his%20first%20fifty%20contained%20no%20fours%20but%20still%20he%20managed%20to%20maintain%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20above%20180%20during%20that%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifty%2C%20the%20right-hander's%2017th%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20came%20off%20just%2028%20balls.%20The%20most%20spectacular%20shot%20that%20Gaikwad%20played%20on%20the%20night%20was%20a%20slice-cut%20off%20pacer%20Mohsin%20Khan%20that%20beat%20the%20point%20fielder%20for%20a%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20focus%20was%20also%20on%20constructing%20useful%20alliances%20with%20his%20teammates%20as%2045%20runs%20were%20made%20with%20Daryl%20Mitchell%2C%20who%20replaced%20an%20out%20of%20touch%20Rachin%20Ravindra%2C%20and%2052%20were%20made%20alongside%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20(17).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20both%20Mitchell%20(11)%2C%20who%20was%20dropped%20on%20four%2C%20and%20Jadeja%20would%20rue%20missing%20out%20on%20a%20chance%20to%20chip%20in%20with%20a%20far%20bigger%20knock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gaikwad%20was%20the%20main%20contributor%20in%20those%20partnerships%2C%20the%20pressure%20was%20slightly%20lifted%20off%20Gaikwad's%20shoulders%20once%20Dube%20arrived%20at%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-hander%20played%20some%20powerful%20hits%20around%20the%20field%20and%2C%20not%20so%20surprisingly%2C%20fetched%20CSK's%20first%20six%20of%20the%20innings%20in%20the%2013th%20over%20off%20pacer%20Marcus%20Stoinis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20soon%20slammed%20the%20first%20six%20of%20his%20innings%20in%20the%2045th%20ball%20he%20faced%20%E2%80%93pulling%20Stoinis'%20half-tracker%20over%20mid-wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Dube%20seamlessly%20slipped%20into%20his%20six-hitting%20avatar%20and%20pacer%20Yash%20Thakur%20bore%20the%20brunt%20as%20the%20left-hander%20smashed%20him%20for%20three%20successive%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%2C%20who%20reached%2099%20with%20a%20six%20off%20Thakur%20over%20extra%20cover%2C%20reached%20his%20second%20IPL%20hundred%20with%20a%20four%20in%20the%20next%20ball%20off%20the%20same%20bowler%20as%20he%20made%2016%20runs%20in%20the%2018th%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20and%20Dube%20brought%20up%20100%20of%20their%20partnership%20in%20just%2046%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDube%20hammered%20Mohsin%20for%20a%20four%20and%20six%20off%20successive%20balls%20to%20reach%20his%20fifty%20in%2022%20balls%20as%20CSK%20plundered%2071%20runs%20off%20the%20last%20five%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713889140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F06ichmj_ruturaj-gaikwad-ms-dhoni-bcci_625x300_22_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Ffirst-time-in-17-years-ruturaj-gaikwad-breaks-ms-dhonis-record-for-major-feat-as-csk-captain-5507533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20CSK%20captaincy%20from%20Dhoni%20this%20season%2C%20stayed%20unbeaten%20on%20108*%20vs%20LSG%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20match%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anant-Radhika%20to%20get%20married%20on%20July%2012%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713888937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109539411%2Cimgsize-4