ngress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20said%20the%20PM%20should%20stop%20his%20attempts%20at%20dividing%20society%20and%20grant%20him%20time%20so%20that%20he%20can%20explain%20the%20document's%20contents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20speeches%20at%20election%20rallies%20this%20month%2C%20the%20PM%20had%20said%20that%20the%20promises%20made%20in%20Congress'%20manifesto%20were%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20thoughts%20that%20the%20Muslim%20League%20had%20before%20Independence.%20In%20a%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%20on%20Sunday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20also%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20controversy%20by%20claiming%20that%20the%20Congress%20intended%20to%20seize%20people's%20property%20and%20redistribute%20it%20to%20Muslims.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BThey%20will%20not%20even%20leave%20your%20'mangalsutra'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20-%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20constituency%20-%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20took%20all%20the%20allegations%20head-on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20says%20the%20Congress%20Manifesto%20is%20a%20Muslim%20League%20manifesto.%20I%20request%20him%2C%20if%20he%20gives%20me%20time%2C%20I%20will%20take%20our%20manifesto%20and%20explain%20it%20to%20him.%20Where%20are%20we%20saying%20that%20something%20is%20only%20for%20Muslims%3F%20We%20are%20doing%20things%20for%20all.%20Our%20manifesto%20is%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20farmers%2C%20youth%20women%20and%20everybody.%20He%20just%20wants%20to%20divide%20the%20society%20and%20keep%20talking%20about%20Hindu-Muslim%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20president%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Congress'%20promises%20for%20the%20youth%20and%20women%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BYuva%20Nyay%20is%20for%20all.%20Naari%20Shakti%20is%20for%20all.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20for%20Muslims%2C%20not%20only%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20those%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%20It%20is%20for%20all.%20During%20the%20UPA%20era%2C%20we%20have%20given%20some%20rights%20without%20the%20people%20asking%20for%20them.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20was%20given%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20opposed%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%20that%20by%20bringing%20in%20MGNREGA%2C%20Congress%20was%20bringing%20poverty%20to%20the%20country.%20We%20made%20MGNREGA%20a%20right%2C%20education%20a%20right%2C%20food%20security%20a%20right.%20These%20things%20can't%20be%20taken%20away%20even%20if%20PM%20Modi%20and%20(Union%20Home%20Minister)%20Amit%20Shah%20wish%20to%20do%20so.%20These%20are%20permanent%20rights%20brought%20by%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20up%20his%20attack%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20he%20has%20toured%20the%20world%20and%20the%20country%2C%20but%20hasn't%20visited%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20went%20there%2C%20consoled%20the%20people%20and%20told%20them%2C%20'Don't%20lose%20heart.%20I%20am%20there'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20over%20the%20PM's%20%26quot%3Binfiltrator%26quot%3B%20remarks%20has%20continued%20to%20be%20on%20the%20boil.%20While%20the%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20PM%20of%20trying%20to%20play%20a%20communal%20card%20and%20divert%20attention%20from%20issues%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20hit%20back%20and%20said%20that%20the%20PM%20called%20a%20spade%20a%20spade%20and%20echoed%20people's%20sentiments.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20cited%20a%20clip%20from%20a%202006%20speech%20by%20then%20PM%20Manmohan%20Singh%20to%20bolster%20his%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713886980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4d8qg44o_kharge-modi_625x300_23_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n