uot%3BThe%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20betrayed%20the%20country%20and%20have%20once%20again%20come%20to%20you%20with%20their%20false%20manifesto.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20Congress'%20manifesto%2C%20they%20say%20that%20if%20they%20form%20a%20government%2C%20we%20will%20implement%20Sharia%20law.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BYou%20tell%20me%2C%20will%20this%20country%20be%20run%20by%20the%20Constitution%20made%20by%20Baba%20Saheb%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20or%20by%20Shariat%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20in%20his%20election%20rallies%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20included%20redistribution%20of%20people's%20property%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20people%20talk%20in%20their%20manifesto%20that%20they%20will%20implement%20'vyaktigat%20kanoon'%20(personal%20laws).%20That%20means%20Sharia%20law%20will%20be%20implemented%20because%20Modi%20ji%20stopped%20the%20practice%20of%20triple%20talaq%2C%26quot%3B%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20say%20that%20we%20will%20again%20restore%20personal%20law.%20These%20people%20will%20implement%20Sharia%20law...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEscalating%20his%20attack%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20alleged%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20manifesto%20says%20that%20they%20will%20take%20people's%20property%20and%20distribute%20it.%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20allow%20the%20Congress%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20to%20loot%20your%20property%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20condition%20of%20these%20shameless%20people.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20they%20are%20eying%20on%20your%20property%20and%20the%20other%20hand%20they%20are%20making%20the%20mafia%20and%20criminals%20their%20necklace%20and%20reciting%20Fatiha%20in%20their%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20a%20comment%20made%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20in%202006%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20ji%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20had%20said%20that%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20to%20the%20country's%20resources...%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSo%20where%20will%20our%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%2C%20Kharagvanshis%2C%20Pals%2C%20poor%20and%20farmers%20go%3F%20Where%20will%20the%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20go%2C%20where%20will%20the%20youth%20go%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20claimed%20that%20terrorism%20has%20been%20finished%20in%20India%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20and%20terror%20in%20the%20country%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20people%20were%20afraid.%20After%202014%2C%20terrorism%20was%20controlled%20and%20by%202019%2C%20Modi%20ji%20did%20such%20a%20thing%20that%20the%20root%20of%20terrorism%20Jammu%20Kashmir's%20Article%20370%20was%20abolished.%20Today%20terrorism%20has%20been%20destroyed%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20claimed%20that%20now%20whenever%20there%20is%20a%20loud%20burst%20of%20firecrackers%20somewhere%2C%20Pakistan%20clarifies%20that%20it%20has%20no%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20is%20afraid%20that%20even%20by%20mistake%2C%20a%20terrorist%20incident%20takes%20place%20in%20India%20and%20some%20innocent%20citizen%20is%20killed%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20face%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20at%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Baghpat%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%20the%20Congress%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20rule%20the%20nation%20for%2065%20years%2C%20but%20they%20did%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20also%20used%20the%20occasion%20to%20take%20a%20dig%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20slogan%20of%20poverty%20eradication%20which%20was%20given%20by%20the%20grandmother%20(Indira%20Gandhi)%20is%20now%20being%20repeated%20by%20the%20grandson%20(Rahul%20Gandhi)%20like%20a%20parrot.%20They%20(Congress)%20don't%20have%20any%20vision.%20When%20they%20were%20ousted%20from%20power%20by%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%20they%20again%20remembered%20the%20idea%20of%20eradicating%20poverty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20truly%20done%20the%20work%20of%20eradicating%20poverty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20while%20seeking%20votes%20for%20NDA%20candidate%20Rajkumar%20Sangwan%20(of%20RLD)%20said%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20do%20dynastic%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SP%20gave%20all%20tickets%20to%20its%20own%20family%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20said%20if%20votes%20go%20to%20the%20wrong%20place%2C%20terrorism%20and%20mafia%20rule%20will%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rights%20of%20farmers%20and%20the%20poor%20will%20again%20be%20subject%20to%20robbery.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20our%20daughters%20and%20the%20businessman%20will%20again%20be%20unsafe%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20cast%20our%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20terrorism%20will%20be%20eliminated%20across%20the%20border%20and%20mafia%20and%20criminals%20in%20the%20country%20will%20be%20sent%20on%20the%20journey%20of%20ram%20naam%20satya%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20president%20Jayant%20Chaudhury%20was%20also%20present%20on%20this%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmroha%20and%20Baghpat%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20on%20April%2026.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published