d%20that%20he%20had%20said%20this%20to%20Congress'%20'%3Cem%3Eshahzada%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(prince)%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3E'shahzada'%3C%2Fem%3E%20jibe%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20Congress'%20%26quot%3Bdynastic%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20been%20regularly%20used%20by%20the%20PM%20to%20refer%20to%20Wayanad%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20not%20an%20insult%20to%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20Constitution%3F%20Is%20this%20not%20meddling%20with%20the%20Constitution%3F%20This%20is%20all%20part%20of%20a%20well-thought-out%20conspiracy%20to%20break%20the%20country.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20negating%20the%20Constitution%20in%20Goa%2C%20tomorrow%20they%20will%20try%20to%20negate%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution%20all%20over%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20remarks%20are%20significant%20because%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20wanting%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20is%20elected%20for%20a%20third%20term.%20This%20was%20also%20stated%20by%20BJP's%20six-time%20MP%20from%20the%20Uttara%20Kannada%20constituency%2C%20Anant%20Hegde%2C%20who%20had%20said%20the%20party%20had%20set%20a%20target%20of%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20for%20the%20NDA%20so%20that%20the%20Constitution%20could%20be%20amended.%20After%20the%20comment%2C%20Mr%20Hegde%20was%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20Congress'%20charge%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLeave%20aside%20the%20BJP%2C%20even%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20himself%20cannot%20abolish%20the%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Someone%20Else%20Decided%20Destiny'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fernandes%2C%20who%20had%20met%20Mr%20Gandhi%20as%20part%20of%20an%20NGO%2C%20'Goencho%20Away'%2C%20which%20was%20pressing%20for%20dual%20citizenship%20f