%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20rich%20source%20of%20protein%2C%20offer%20curd%2C%20eggs%20and%20paneer.%20Add%20nut%20butters%20and%20nut%20powders%20in%20porridges%2C%20dosas%2C%20fruits%20to%20ensure%20a%20complete%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEasy%20to%20make%20cereal%20mixes%20at%20home%2Fduring%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20experts%20advise%20parents%20to%20use%20millets%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20superfoods%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20great%20for%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20roast%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erava%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Epoha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20oats%20and%20other%20millets%2C%20and%20then%20powder%20them%20separately.%20Just%20mix%20with%20hot%20water%2C%20add%20a%20fruit%20if%20you%20wish%2C%20and%20an%20instant%20porridge%20is%20ready.%20They%20are%20great%20for%20travel%20too.%20You%20can%20also%20add%20mango%2C%20banana%2C%20apples%2C%20berries%20to%20sweeten%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Divisha%20Jadhwani%2C%20a%20baby%20and%20child%20nutritionist.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20good%20option%20for%20Indian%20households%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290986%2Fhemapriya-natesan-sathumaavu-traditional-powder-for-babies-no-sugar-startup-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esattu%20maavu%20%3C%2Fem%3E(multigrain)%20mix%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20of%20these%20powders%20and%20mixes%20are%20sold%20by%20homegrown%20brands%20in%20case%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20snacks%2C%20you%20could%20try%20%3Cem%3Emurmuras%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emakhanas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20puffed%20%3Cem%3Erajgira%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20jowar%20puffs%2C%20ragi%20puffs%2C%20laddoos%2C%20and%20homemade%20cookies.%20All%20these%20can%20also%20be%20carried%20during%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%E2%80%99