Institute%20of%20Mass%20Communication%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20Samyak%20began%20to%20get%20invested%20in%20current%20affairs%2C%20particularly%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20of%202019.%20Intent%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20mechanism%20creating%20change%20in%20society%2C%20Samyak%20decided%20to%20follow%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281857%2Fupsc-cse-interview-topper-ias-apala-mishra-score-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalling%20of%20joining%20the%20civil%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20registered%20for%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20saw%20this%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20getting%20direct%20agency%20that%20would%20help%20him%20ease%20the%20plight%20of%20people%2C%20and%20make%20a%20tangible%20difference%20to%20society.%20And%20this%20is%20exactly%20the%20message%20he%20is%20upholding%20in%20his%20current%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20dreams%20to%20create%20impact%20in%20areas%20of%20pollution%2C%20traffic%20management%2C%20and%20education%2C%20Samyak%20speaks%20of%20how%20losing%20your%20vision%20can%20change%20the%20trajectory%20of%20your%20life.%20%E2%80%9CChallenging%20circumstances%20can%20either%20break%20you%20or%20make%20you.%20Always%20choose%20the%20latter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713768301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-17-115409-1713335091.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samyak%20Jain's%20journey%20to%20securing%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%207%20in%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20was%20fueled%20by%20resilience%20despite%20facing%20progressive%20vision%20loss.%20Today%2C%20as%20an%20Assistant%20Collector%20of%2