k%20and%20gives%20a%20good%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20am%20extremely%20happy%20to%20reap%20benefits%20by%20adopting%20this%20new%20technique%2C%20initially%20I%20made%20some%20mistakes%20in%20getting%20good%20nutrients%20from%20the%20market.%20I%20got%20misled%20into%20buying%20nutrients%20from%20fraud%20companies.%20This%20delayed%20my%20production%20by%201.5%20months.%20But%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20the%20next%20season%20from%20the%20same%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dheeraj%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20cultivating%20red%20and%20yellow%20varieties%20of%20capsicum%20on%20the%20hydroponics%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20his%20example%2C%20Dheeraj%20advises%20other%20farmers%20to%20explore%20hydroponics%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20technique%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20any%20untutored%20farmer%20can%20reap%20handsome%20profits%20with%20hydroponics%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dheeraj%20Verma.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713767578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-1-1713533722.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Encouraged%20by%20the%20soil-less%20farming%20technique%20used%20in%20Israel%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Dheeraj%20Verma%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20strawberries%20using%20hydroponics.%20He%20earned%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20just%20two%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347819%2Fstrawberry-farming-in-uttar-pradesh-hydroponics-farm-in-barabanki-earns-farmer-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Architect%E2%80%9